metadata.name: Resilience #102
metadata.description:
In this project i tried to portray the struggles and hardships of life in a modern era. The use of bold and gloomy shades of black, brown and gray creates an overwhelming sense of oppression and heaviness. Yet amidst the chaos, tiny specks of light in the form of vibrant, bright colors like red, gold, yellow, green and blue symbolize hope and resilience.

The texture is heavily layered, suggesting the layers of difficulties that must be faced and overcome in life.

Overall, this canvas captures the essence of a hard life, but also highlights the triumphs of the human spirit in the face of adversity.

metadata.name: We Are Alone Together #99
metadata.description:
We meander through the flows of life, alone but together. This experience — an ultimately solitary one — is communicated but never truly shared. Our consciousnesses live in a perpetual separated state, alone but together.

metadata.name: Geo #50
metadata.description:
🥳 HAPPY BIRTHDAY FXHASH 🥳
  
This work consists of 9 different frames in total and there are 30 different drawings for each frame. Mathematically there are 1.9683e+13 different variations. Only certain works have the number 1 in the middle. If you are feeling lucky, you will see the number 1 in the middle square :)

- Each frame is hand drawn.

- Image Size = 1500*1500

Thank you for supporting my work in the first year of fxhash. It was a life changing experience for me. Congratulations to the artists, collectors and developers on a great year!

This work participates in the FxHash anniversary event (#fxhashturnsone) and 20% of royalties and all secondary sales go to Save Pakistan.

A selection of rare palettes
And a smaller set of ultra rare palettes

metadata.name: Clouds over the Mountains #233
metadata.description:
“I'd go as far as the end of a stream or fountain, 
And sit and gaze on cloud rising over the mountain.” 
— Wang Wei (Tang dynasty)

「行到水窮處，坐看雲起時。」
—— 唐·王維

This artwork is inspired by the poem above, and creates a view to “gaze on cloud rising over the mountain”. 
This is also a tribute to the traditional Chinese landscape painting. 

☁️☁️☁️☁️
⛰️⛰️⛰️⛰️

It takes time to generate. Run on a computer for better experience. 
Student of @Newyellow. Made with p5js.

metadata.name: (fx)moji #115
metadata.description:
Emoji is the word for visual language, a way to express emotion without words.

From its humble origins as a Japanese emoticon in the mid-1990s, they exploded in popularity when appeared as a critical part of Apple's iPhone launch in 2007. The internationalization of emoji is an inexorable force, and today it is almost impossible to send a message without using one.

Emojis evolved as a way to communicate quickly and easily, and now they will evolve one more time and become an NFT generative art reborn as (fx)moji where basic geometric forms create a new full set of emojis expressions.

32 emojis,
7 Animations,
6 Color &
Infinite expressions 😊

Made with love ❤️ 🧡 💛 💚 💙 and p5js
